name: napari-layer-table
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "napari-layer-table" %}
{% set version = "0.0.7" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/napari-layer-table-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 21538e5877c493050bd2c24b4191ae55f390a9a5c22afc3f2e62da986870fe48

build:
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.7
  run:
    - napari
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - python >=3.7
    - qtpy

test:
  imports:
    - napari_layer_table
  commands:
    - pip list
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/mapmanager/napari-layer-table
  summary: A plugin to display a layer as a table.
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - cudmore
    - goanpeca
    - jaimergp
